This software is a implement of the paper "High-Performance Batch Exponentiation Outsourcing with Checkability and its Application for IoT Environment".
Which is published on the ESTSD, 2017.

To run this java project, you need to have the Java Pairing Based Cryptography Library(jPBC) installed (jpbc-2.0.0 is tested). 
You can get it from the following page:
   	・ http://gas.dia.unisa.it/projects/jpbc/
and my java version is 9.0.1.

Thanks for junwei-wang who provide the similar cpabe open-source-code on githob:
	・ https://github.com/junwei-wang/cpabe
	・ Junwei Wang. Java Realization for Ciphertext-Policy Attribute-Based Encryption. https://github.com/junwei-wang/cpabe/, 2012
	
and much other code is referenced from the Internet, i had commented before the line.



